         <p>Arranged by family member.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_75d1be22f241a90c4a9750056b6ce704">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection consists chiefly of legal papers of various members of the Bushnell Family of Saybrook, Connecticut. Most of the legal documents relate to the purchase of land and other financial transactions. Also included are the compositions of Lydia O. Dibble, a cousin of Ida Bushnell.</p>
         <p>A small amount of the Bushnell Family Papers were transferred from the Yale Divinity School. The majority were received from an unknown donor in 1969.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
